OL,5, A "perfect storm" of problems led to a 
OL,6, family grieving at the wrong grave for 
OL,7, 17 years, an inquiry has found.        
OL,9,FThe Bell family found the headstone for
OL,10,Ftheir father Thomas had been put on the
OL,11,Fwrong grave at Holy Trinity in Wingate,
OL,12,FCounty Durham in 2005, when they went  
OL,13,Fto bury his wife Hilda in June.        
OL,15,FA church probe found records had been  
OL,16,Fpoorly kept.                           
OL,18,FThe report said it could not guarantee 
OL,19,Fother historic errors had not been     
OL,20,Fmade.                                  
